<div class="content"><p>The LINE_MONITORTONE packet is sent when a tone is detected.
The sending of this packet is controlled with the <a href="7c865cf1-5d68-41cc-bd61-928603d34d94" data-linktype="relative-path">MonitorTones</a> packet. The
LINE_MONITORTONE packet is sent if client has requested the tone be monitored.</p><table>
